### Appendix B: Dataset Construction

#### B.1 Diverse Benign Sources (5,905 prompts after deduplication)

| Source | Approx N | Mean length | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| WildChat | 1500 | 200-2000 chars | Real user conversations (Anthropic-style) |
| OR-Bench Hard | 1000 | 60-300 chars | Edge-case benign (looks suspicious) |
| MMLU | 1000 | 100-500 chars | Factual queries across domains |
| GSM8K | 500 | 100-300 chars | Math word problems |
| HumanEval | 164 | 80-200 chars | Code generation (Python) |
| MBPP | 374 | 80-200 chars | Code generation (Python) |
| WikiText long-form | 800 | 1500-15000 chars | Matches puzzler/saa attack lengths |
| Multilingual subset | 200 | varied | Cross-lingual test |
| Alpaca control | 367 | 50-100 chars | Original setup for backwards compat |

#### B.2 Length Distribution

- Mean: 1,076 chars
- Median: 179 chars
- Max: 18,205 chars
- >2,000 chars: 752 prompts
- >5,000 chars: 354 prompts

