Released at github.com/NISPLab/JBShield. 9 categories per LLM:

| Attack | N (Llama-3) | N (Vicuna-13B) | Mean length |
|---|---|---|---|
| autodan | 850 | 850 | 77 chars |
| base64 | 850 | 850 | 124 chars |
| drattack | 520 | 520 | 437 chars |
| gcg | 850 | 850 | 35 chars |
| ijp | 821 | 821 | 460 chars |
| pair | 850 | 850 | 72 chars |
| puzzler | 50 | 50 | 2,193 chars |
| saa | 834 | 834 | 473 chars |
| zulu | 849 | 849 | 50 chars |

After deduplication (15 train/test overlapping prompts removed):
- Llama-3 attacks: 6,474 unique → 5,179 train + 1,295 test
- Vicuna attacks: 6,474 unique → 5,180 train + 1,294 test

